## Limitations

The report is based on available online sources and may not capture the full scope of academic research on the topic. Additionally, the rapid evolution of cell phone technology means that some findings may become outdated as new features and applications are developed. Further research could explore the long-term societal impacts of cell phone usage, particularly in emerging markets where adoption rates are increasing.